{
  "id": "2021-11-08_screen_english",
  "date": "2021-11-08",
  "corner": "screen_english",
  "corner_label": "Screen English",
  "title": "He wanted to please you",
  "movie": "",
  "duration_sec": 673.92,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2021-11-08_screen_english.mp3",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.18,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.18,
      "end": 25.29,
      "text": "영화 감상과 영화 공부를 동시에 스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.29,
      "end": 28.53,
      "text": "11월에 함께하고 있는 영화는 갈매기"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.53,
      "end": 29.67,
      "text": "The Seagull"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.67,
      "end": 30.07,
      "text": "입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.07,
      "end": 31.39,
      "text": "어서오세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.39,
      "end": 31.93,
      "text": "Hello"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.93,
      "end": 32.83,
      "text": "Good morning"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.83,
      "end": 34.45,
      "text": "Good morning, how's it going?"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.85,
      "end": 36.79,
      "text": "Everything is okay, how about you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.97,
      "end": 39.01,
      "text": "Everything is okay here too"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.01,
      "end": 42.05,
      "text": "네, 아주 즐거운 분위기로 시작을 하고 있네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.05,
      "end": 42.47,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.47,
      "end": 44.75,
      "text": "4862님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.75,
      "end": 46.65,
      "text": "조크쌤 하트"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.65,
      "end": 48.75,
      "text": "아침의 시작을 함께하겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.75,
      "end": 51.11,
      "text": "하트, 땡큐 so much"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.11,
      "end": 52.19,
      "text": "하트, 하트, 하트, 하트"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.19,
      "end": 54.01,
      "text": "Oh, thank you so much"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.01,
      "end": 55.53,
      "text": "아, 참 기분 좋네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.53,
      "end": 56.49,
      "text": "That's a lot of hearts"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.49,
      "end": 57.85,
      "text": "A lot of love"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.85,
      "end": 59.43,
      "text": "이렇게 하트를 많이 받으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.43,
      "end": 62.27,
      "text": "정말 가슴 속에 사랑이 충만해지는 느낌입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.27,
      "end": 63.95,
      "text": "Yes, we're confident"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.95,
      "end": 65.39,
      "text": "We're full of love"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.39,
      "end": 69.07,
      "text": "이제 본격적으로 영화 속의 내용을 알아볼 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.07,
      "end": 71.35,
      "text": "이미 말씀을 몇 번 드린 것처럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.35,
      "end": 73.27,
      "text": "This movie was actually based on"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.27,
      "end": 76.39,
      "text": "아주 유명한 극작가 있잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.39,
      "end": 77.01,
      "text": "Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.01,
      "end": 77.39,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.39,
      "end": 78.37,
      "text": "Anton Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.37,
      "end": 80.33,
      "text": "I got his name down right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.33,
      "end": 82.81,
      "text": "Yeah, 그 러시안 작가인"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.81,
      "end": 83.57,
      "text": "Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.57,
      "end": 84.57,
      "text": "Yeah, Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.57,
      "end": 87.47,
      "text": "네, 이분의 작품을 바탕으로 만들어졌는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.47,
      "end": 89.05,
      "text": "흥미롭게도"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.05,
      "end": 90.71,
      "text": "There's always been some characters"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.71,
      "end": 94.59,
      "text": "who are very weak and incompetent"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.59,
      "end": 95.93,
      "text": "Incompetent, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.05,
      "end": 96.57,
      "text": "Incompetent"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.57,
      "end": 97.99,
      "text": "Yeah, incompetent"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.99,
      "end": 99.07,
      "text": "Yeah, 능력하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.07,
      "end": 101.47,
      "text": "Weak, incompetent"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.47,
      "end": 102.55,
      "text": "Depressed"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.55,
      "end": 104.59,
      "text": "Kind of gloomy"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.59,
      "end": 107.65,
      "text": "항상 이런 등장인물들이 많이 등장을 하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.65,
      "end": 109.11,
      "text": "Just the same as this one"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.11,
      "end": 109.59,
      "text": "갈매기"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.59,
      "end": 110.13,
      "text": "Same here"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.13,
      "end": 110.47,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.47,
      "end": 111.73,
      "text": "And it's funny actually"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.73,
      "end": 112.35,
      "text": "Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.35,
      "end": 114.61,
      "text": "He called this play a comedy"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.61,
      "end": 116.49,
      "text": "He said this is a comedy"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.49,
      "end": 117.11,
      "text": "그런데"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.11,
      "end": 118.79,
      "text": "comedy 같은 느낌은"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.79,
      "end": 120.29,
      "text": "크다지 많이 있진 않았어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.29,
      "end": 121.15,
      "text": "I'm not an expert"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.15,
      "end": 123.59,
      "text": "But it does not seem at all"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.59,
      "end": 125.41,
      "text": "Like a comedy to me"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.41,
      "end": 127.25,
      "text": "It seems more tragic"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.25,
      "end": 127.69,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.69,
      "end": 128.91,
      "text": "Very depressing"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.91,
      "end": 130.39,
      "text": "저도 마찬가지로"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.39,
      "end": 132.75,
      "text": "But I guess he tries to find comedy"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.75,
      "end": 134.95,
      "text": "In the conflict"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.95,
      "end": 135.95,
      "text": "So"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.95,
      "end": 137.15,
      "text": "Let's figure it out"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.15,
      "end": 137.61,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.61,
      "end": 138.77,
      "text": "We'll figure it out together"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.77,
      "end": 139.05,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.05,
      "end": 140.31,
      "text": "이 갈매기가"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.31,
      "end": 141.97,
      "text": "이 Chekhov의"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.97,
      "end": 144.55,
      "text": "첫 성공을 거둔 작품이라면서요"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.55,
      "end": 144.99,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.19,
      "end": 146.55,
      "text": "Yeah, he wrote it"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.55,
      "end": 147.45,
      "text": "in 1895"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.45,
      "end": 149.09,
      "text": "And then it premiered"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.09,
      "end": 150.39,
      "text": "In 1896"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.39,
      "end": 152.79,
      "text": "And it was its first successful"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.79,
      "end": 154.37,
      "text": "dramatic play"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.37,
      "end": 154.99,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.99,
      "end": 155.77,
      "text": "It wasn't"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.77,
      "end": 157.37,
      "text": "At first it wasn't successful"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.37,
      "end": 159.43,
      "text": "I'll tell you about that later"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.43,
      "end": 159.95,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.95,
      "end": 160.57,
      "text": "But"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.57,
      "end": 162.71,
      "text": "It became a huge success"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.71,
      "end": 164.23,
      "text": "And now actually"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.23,
      "end": 166.43,
      "text": "I heard that the seagull"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.43,
      "end": 168.87,
      "text": "Or a bird that looks like a seagull"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.87,
      "end": 171.63,
      "text": "Is the actual symbol of theater"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.63,
      "end": 173.79,
      "text": "And plays in Russia"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.79,
      "end": 174.71,
      "text": "그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.79,
      "end": 176.23,
      "text": "러시아에 진짜 있어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.33,
      "end": 176.97,
      "text": "상징처럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.97,
      "end": 178.29,
      "text": "A common symbol"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.29,
      "end": 178.71,
      "text": "와"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.71,
      "end": 180.25,
      "text": "그만큼 영향력을"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.25,
      "end": 181.63,
      "text": "끼친 작품이었나 보네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.63,
      "end": 182.69,
      "text": "Huge success"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.69,
      "end": 184.37,
      "text": "One of the top plays"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.37,
      "end": 185.17,
      "text": "in all of Russia"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.17,
      "end": 188.03,
      "text": "그래서 연극을 배우는 사람들이라면"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.03,
      "end": 189.81,
      "text": "반드시 꼭 한 번은"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.81,
      "end": 191.45,
      "text": "거쳐가는 작품이라고 하더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.45,
      "end": 192.53,
      "text": "그래서 우리나라에도"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.53,
      "end": 194.07,
      "text": "연극 무대에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.07,
      "end": 195.99,
      "text": "자주 올려지는 작품이라고 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.99,
      "end": 196.31,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.31,
      "end": 197.37,
      "text": "I wonder if they have it"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.37,
      "end": 198.27,
      "text": "in 대항로"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.27,
      "end": 198.71,
      "text": "음"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.71,
      "end": 200.01,
      "text": "아마 있지 않을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.31,
      "end": 200.89,
      "text": "Maybe"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.89,
      "end": 202.41,
      "text": "We should go check it out"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.41,
      "end": 204.15,
      "text": "We can watch a live performance"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.15,
      "end": 205.07,
      "text": "in Korean"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.07,
      "end": 206.27,
      "text": "of the seagull"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.27,
      "end": 207.21,
      "text": "대항로"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.21,
      "end": 207.87,
      "text": "안 가본지가"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.87,
      "end": 208.15,
      "text": "진짜"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.15,
      "end": 209.71,
      "text": "It's been a really long time"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.71,
      "end": 211.61,
      "text": "진짜 오래 전에 갔었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.61,
      "end": 212.39,
      "text": "It's been ages"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.39,
      "end": 213.33,
      "text": "You're too"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.33,
      "end": 213.93,
      "text": "Me too"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.93,
      "end": 214.61,
      "text": "기회가 되면"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.61,
      "end": 215.97,
      "text": "한번 가보면 좋겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.97,
      "end": 218.7,
      "text": "오늘 장면 듣고 올게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.7,
      "end": 219.6,
      "text": "Heaven's sake"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.6,
      "end": 220.88,
      "text": "He wanted to please you"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.88,
      "end": 222.4,
      "text": "And I was willing"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.4,
      "end": 223.2,
      "text": "to listen"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.2,
      "end": 224.68,
      "text": "even to his ravings"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.68,
      "end": 224.96,
      "text": "but"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.96,
      "end": 226.2,
      "text": "his claims"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.2,
      "end": 226.96,
      "text": "to new forms"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.96,
      "end": 227.82,
      "text": "they're pretentious"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.82,
      "end": 229.8,
      "text": "Since when has the exhibition"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.8,
      "end": 231.72,
      "text": "of a morbid personality"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.72,
      "end": 232.96,
      "text": "been a new art form?"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.58,
      "end": 234.46,
      "text": "Everyone writes"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.46,
      "end": 235.26,
      "text": "what he wants"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.26,
      "end": 236.42,
      "text": "and as best he can"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.42,
      "end": 239.0,
      "text": "What's going on?"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.42,
      "end": 240.82,
      "text": "이 컨스탄티니어"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.82,
      "end": 242.22,
      "text": "just stopped everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.22,
      "end": 243.32,
      "text": "with anger"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.32,
      "end": 245.02,
      "text": "He was performing"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.02,
      "end": 246.18,
      "text": "his play"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.18,
      "end": 247.52,
      "text": "by the lake"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.52,
      "end": 249.24,
      "text": "in the night time"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.24,
      "end": 249.64,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.64,
      "end": 250.42,
      "text": "And he stopped"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.42,
      "end": 251.4,
      "text": "in the middle of the play"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.4,
      "end": 252.56,
      "text": "and ran away"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.56,
      "end": 253.88,
      "text": "이게 무슨 일입니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.14,
      "end": 254.5,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.64,
      "end": 255.66,
      "text": "저는 이 장면을 보면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.66,
      "end": 256.84,
      "text": "it was so shocking"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.84,
      "end": 257.6,
      "text": "It was"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.6,
      "end": 259.46,
      "text": "진짜 너무 충격적인 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.46,
      "end": 260.64,
      "text": "이라고 생각을 했었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.64,
      "end": 261.64,
      "text": "Did you see"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.64,
      "end": 263.1,
      "text": "while they were performing"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.1,
      "end": 263.64,
      "text": "the play"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.64,
      "end": 265.9,
      "text": "the two people"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.9,
      "end": 267.7,
      "text": "His mom"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.7,
      "end": 269.26,
      "text": "Constantine's mom"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.26,
      "end": 270.22,
      "text": "She was sitting"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.22,
      "end": 271.16,
      "text": "in the front row"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.16,
      "end": 272.76,
      "text": "and she was making"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.76,
      "end": 274.28,
      "text": "wisecracks"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.28,
      "end": 276.5,
      "text": "sarcastic remarks"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.5,
      "end": 277.7,
      "text": "that were not"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.7,
      "end": 278.86,
      "text": "very pleasant"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.86,
      "end": 280.1,
      "text": "and I think"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.1,
      "end": 281.34,
      "text": "he overheard those"
